    "rationale": "Based on review of the available simulation evidence and Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification results, the CFD model is considered adequate for predicting absolute hemolysis levels for the VAD COU. The model demonstrated acceptable agreement with experimental hemolysis data across the primary operating conditions, and uncertainty bounds remain within clinically acceptable margins. The assessment team concludes that the overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support regulatory submission.",
